# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/2.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## {0.1.4} - 2026-06-20

### Fixed

- use `$collection->id()` instead of `$collection->name()` to only get the collection name and not the full path.

## [0.1.3] - 2026-06-20

### Changed

- Use `SharedKernel` only as dev dependency to prevent multiple instances of `EntityRegistry`.

## [0.1.2] - 2026-06-20

### Changed

- Update `SharedKernel` version.

## [0.1.1] - 2026-06-20

### Fixed

- Remove `final` from `FirestoreDAO` definition.

## [0.1.0] - 2026-06-19

### Added

- Added `FirestoreDAO`.

